value.0: A searing shaft of white light descends from some unseen place above.
Once there was more cave here but no more. That said its clear someone is digging here to expand.. Are those claw marks?
Ladder to a hatch thats closed and cant be opend at this time.

At Night and clear sky moonlight shines trough a series of narrow openings on these herbs growing here. Its clear this along some other secrets makes a far more potent and blessed, belladonna or Wolfs-bane.

Refined and pressed into a liquid, this belladonna extract is extremely potent compared to the raw herb.

Its just sitting here on the table for later use. Will you leave it or steal it? It sure would come in handy.. But the owner might need it, dilemmas..
